common gcc options:
-pedantic-errors -Wall -Wextra -Wshadow -Wpointer-arith -Wcast-qual -Wstrict-prototypes -Wstrict-aliasing=2 -Wold-style-definition -Wredundant-decls -Wlogical-op -Wunreachable-code -Wundef -Winline -Wbad-function-cast -Wcast-align -Wno-unused-function -Wno-unused-parameter -Wmisleading-indentation -O2 -Wall -std=c11

debug:
-fsanitize=undefined -fno-sanitize-recover

some gcc options for shared library:
-fPIC (not -fpic)
